## Tabs — pill spring

```tsx
<motion.div
  className="pointer-events-none absolute rounded-[9999px]"
  animate={{ left: pillLeft, width: pillWidth }}
  transition={{ type: "spring", stiffness: 420, damping: 30, mass: 0.8 }}
  style={{ top: 6, bottom: 6, background: "#F68D3D" }}
/>
```

Container: bg `#FFFFFF`, `rounded-[20px]`, `p-1.5`.
Botões inativos: hover areia `rgba(213,210,201,0.35)`.

